---
const sampleFormUrl = "https://naver.me/GqfJUJaH";
const kakaoUrl = "https://open.kakao.com/o/sx6KEqpi";
---

<footer id="contact" class="site-footer">
    <section class="contact-cta container" aria-label="상담 문의">
        <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
            <h2>프로젝트 상담을 시작해보세요</h2>
            <p>제품 사진, 도면, 수량만 알려주시면 제작 방향을 빠르게 안내해드립니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-actions">
            <a href={kakaoUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="footer-button footer-button-primary">카카오톡 문의</a>
            <a href={sampleFormUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="footer-button">샘플신청</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="container footer-grid">
        <div>
            <h2>Label Lab</h2>
            <p>경남 창원시 성산구 가양로 34번길 5-36</p>
            <p>사업자번호: 712-81-02811</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3>연락처</h3>
            <p>전화: 055-262-2701</p>
            <p>이메일: labellabsales@naver.com</p>
            <p>평일 09:00 - 18:00</p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3>우리의 약속</h3>
            <p>빠른 대응</p>
            <p>경쟁력있는 가격</p>
            <p>낮은 최소주문량</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    .site-footer {
        margin-top: var(--space-xl);
        padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
        background: var(--text-heading);
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
    }

    .contact-cta {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 0.6fr;
        gap: var(--space-lg);
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
        padding: var(--space-lg);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    }

    .contact-cta h2 {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
        font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .contact-cta p {
        max-width: 620px;
    }

    .contact-actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        gap: var(--space-sm);
    }

    .footer-button {
        display: inline-flex;
        min-height: 48px;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 12px 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 900;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
    }

    .footer-button-primary {
        border-color: transparent;
        background: var(--color-primary);
    }

    .footer-button-primary:hover {
        background: var(--color-primary-hover);
    }

    .footer-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    h2,
    h3 {
        margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    p {
        margin: 4px 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .contact-cta {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .contact-actions {
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }

        .footer-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
